channel.title: How to fix Miss Silabsoft's Web-Client
channel.description:
1. www.uppit.com/KO3EYP for .silabclient_store_32 Note: New to the word above the Image thing.
2. Download the folder to Desktop.
3. Move folder to C:\WINDOWS\, located: Local Disk-HPc
4. Restart computer for full completion.
5. If having connection problem's try restarting your computer, If that doesn't work, sorry.
